reviews.text: The queue is always so long, I understand the food is good but then I can't wait 20 mins for a fast food restaurant.
It was renovated not long ago.  Nice place to sit down to enjoy the KFC chicken.

This shop has been recently renovated, the table setting was a bit better than before. Have ordered the new Sakura fried chicken set. A bit sweet and taste seemed strange. Prefer the classic ones or the spicy chicken. One thing that I could not understand, the queue of ordering food was usually long even there were few people. The staff's reaction and pace was just too slow making the customers waited unnecessarily...
Clean and tidy fast food shop. Service is good and efficient. Price is reasonably low.
The chicken is amazing and the soft drinks are good

reviews.text: kfc已經 冇得出巴辣雞粒， 巴辣雞粒最好食嘅辣醬油冇 唯有以後少啲幫襯
這餐廳在商場2樓，面積不大。KFC 的鬆餅的味道大不如前。但是，燒雞排的水準依然較其他快餐店出色。
不錯, 唔多人, 可能當天是星期日, 工業區商業區會少人, 新地筒好食過對面麥記
改用自動售賣機之後效率快了非常多，應該早就轉用。
Lunch time 只可以叫外賣 好難有位

reviews.text: Fully-featured mall - great if you're living nearby and don't want to travel too far.
Spacious mall with food outlets and restaurants. Right on MTR station

A medium size mall serving the local communities with some inexpensive eateries too.  Some craftsmanship stalls too.  Just 5 min walk from the nearest metro station.  Built some 2 decades ago and thus a very humble mall but lots of local characteristics.
Have several restaurants and fast food shop here. Not too much shops and therefore it is not really a shopping mall!
Basic mall for fast food only

reviews.text: 各式商鋪齊全👍
這商場雖然不算大，但食肆很多，只是酒樓已有三間。面積雖小但不算太擠廹因很少國內自由行的遊客！一般商場應有的設施它都有，所以亦算方便！
廣埸內有大家樂 麥當勞 肯德基 太興 及兩間酒樓， 一間是潮式酒樓。廣場辦公時間比較旺，也有其他商鋪及銀行， 但不多。
